{"tid":1373623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話和理非係盾，就唔該真係用翻嚟保護前線","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:55:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T16:12:58.000Z","uid":110915,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3cca7ec88573de108c8fd42fea413a31434cb86","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"文宣成日都話和理非係盾，但究竟和理非幾時真係好好咁盡咗個盾嘅責任。<br />\n既然講得做盾，佢嘅作用自然係用嚟保護前線勇武嘅手足，而唔係因為驚個盾會爛而叫你應該保護嘅人跟住你撤、跟住你走。<br />\n如果各位真係想做個稱職嘅盾，要做嘅唔係聽到有人嗌走就一齊走，而係幫手確保勇武手足佢地想落咩決定嘅時候可以無憂無慮。<br />\n當前線話想留，就確保現場有足夠嘅人去backup；當前線話想走，就確保佢地可以無後顧之憂咁走。<br />\n下次再聽到有唔知邊度嘅人話要走嘅時候，除非係你面前嘅勇武都話要走，否則大家要做嘅唔係一齊嗌人走，而係一齊守住所有可行嘅退路。大家要等最前線知道，佢地後面已經係絕對嘅安全，就算發生咩事，佢地都有路可退、有路可走，咁樣先係真正嘅「一齊嚟、一齊走」。<br />\n最後，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ed31fefd64a036932e1b9ddef4cb1dbe8f6f95bd","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:04:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"239b7dc4c0bef617db5a25b19dca19bf0c0bd1c6","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"181a2adaa481ae404d19cb4c2f923bb6b2bf2e94","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:04:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"ccbfa44f4226510fc32e347d9f641f65d2387aea","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"8ae0359aa248b4822e3187adcfec0a1226878901","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"91ac382c67fdfa2df49f479e42483fa5bb9d6d08","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"459380d8dfbdf2cfc3c62c572df703a425b20b71","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:05:59.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"e227d1bf8e0970020431c0dbd9d79b7c4a9f80d2","tid":1373623,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:07.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"cbd21d297aa875371347053730ae432ce02191b3","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"77d07cecbfae752f7d92b7fd5825bb3fc47dfb6f","tid":1373623,"uid":140326,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:23.000Z","msg":"勇武決定左要留，已經做好比攻擊準備，<br />\n真正留喺現場嘅勇武兄弟，係唔會怪自已人離開，<br />\n即使離開現場，和理非心中都會支持留守兄弟決定，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留下：支持；離開：專重</span></span><br />\n有班3毛扮勇武屌自己人散水，<br />\n和理非唔好被影響到<br />\n<br />\n勇武其實已經有左付死嘅決心，<br />\n死都唔怕，點會怕比人拉同比人打，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武在乎嘅係用自己嘅生命去揭露政權嘅邪惡，</span></span><br />\n我地應該給予最大專重同支持，<br />\n留低嘅人就盡量留到最後，<br />\n直至政府宣布特赦呢班義士為止<br />\n<br />\n【散水】有份叫人730走嘅入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d63c1cb6a457961cb7b30846a568557316f443b","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"0552e6584900d723288be646d923c58c57dfe5b3","tid":1373623,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3eee85bb14fe4b015f201a2506b4e2679ab8fe26","tid":1373623,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fd140df3affc6785a114fa1156e5f36a31ba11e5","tid":1373623,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"c1bbe6ee213e2eac5e85c5e6a3e5e802cc81b0f0","tid":1373623,"uid":19182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dcd237a23996e0b44a99c465dc529132b260362","tid":1373623,"uid":209668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"eb1db650fed83930e67776170930bd265101694e","tid":1373623,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e072b3b634f6c710104f970c7eddf547d71ed4c1","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:07.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f9fb6f33c5684dd4002fdcc8ee830b4f3218b8d6","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"},{"pid":"874a9c318ae8e32f5460143d29c18b462a762557","tid":1373623,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2712719bd51201fbe1b3cbec3c57840eebf36cd9","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"},{"pid":"e3739faea08022d8e8dcd8c69d07d0192d79219e","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"},{"pid":"8ca485444fe13f835be97905f6ad00cd39d809d5","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:09:07.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"},{"pid":"ee9d4ecf79cb594c2d7b7e6d17aebb3fea424fa3","tid":1373623,"uid":110915,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:09:29.000Z","msg":"支持前線決定"}]}